      "description": "Offering a museum-grade A80 Supra Turbo, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six. This specimen remains in its factory-original configuration, with the CT20 turbines providing linear power delivery across the rev range. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. All body panels retain original VIN tags, and the double-wishbone suspension remains tight with no bushing degradation. The engine bay is clinically clean with zero fluid seepage, reflecting a meticulous maintenance history. A rare opportunity to acquire a pristine, unmodified icon of Japanese performance engineering.",
